edu.csus.plugin.securecodingassistant.compilation

Class SecureCompilationParticipant

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jdt.core.compiler.CompilationParticipant
      • edu.csus.plugin.securecodingassistant.compilation.SecureCompilationParticipant

  • public class SecureCompilationParticipant
extends CompilationParticipant
    Uses the NodeVisitor to check each ASTNode to see if an IRule has been violated. Overrides the CompilationParticipant.reconcile(ReconcileContext) method. Adds to an InsecureCodeSegment list.
    Author:
    Ben White
    See Also:
    NodeVisitor, IRule, InsecureCodeSegment
